EmailTemplate.name: HOS confirmation email
EmailTemplate.subject: St Andrew's Cathedral School: Tour Booking Confirmation
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Lead.FirstName}
I am writing to confirm that your booking on our Head of School Tour scheduled for {!Lead.School_Tour_Date__c} at 9.00am, Ground Floor, St Andrew's House, Sydney Square, Sydney (opposite the main entrance to St Andrew's Cathedral - refer map attached). You will be greeted by our staff in the Foyer upon arrival.
Tea, coffee and refreshments will be served from 8.45am.
The tour commences at 9.00am with a welcome from our Head of School, Dr Collier, followed by a tour of the School facilities at both St Andrew's House and our Senior College on Druitt Street.
It is anticipated that the tour will conclude by 10.30am.
To assist in the organisation of the tour, it would be appreciated if you could provide the following information:
1. Number of people attending: {!Lead.No_of_People_Attending__c}
2. Will you be attending with a small child or stroller?
3. Names of people attending: {!Lead.FirstName} {!Lead.LastName}, {!Lead.Other_Tour_Attendee_Name__c}
4. Academic Year and Calendar Year you are considering for your child: Year {!Lead.Year_Group__c} {!Lead.Year_of_Entry__c}
5. How did you find out about St Andrew’s Cathedral School; and
6. Anything you would like covered in the talk or tour?
Please note it is important that you confirm your attendance.
We look forward to welcoming you to St Andrew's Cathedral School.
Kindest regards
Robyn Pedley Enrolments Manager
There is parking available underneath the building in the Wilsons Car Park (entry 464 Kent Street). Commercial rates apply. For further information refer Wilsons Parking website.
St Andrew's Cathedral School
Sydney Square, Sydney NSW 2000, Australia
